contributionDescription: I center my contributions on empowering the Latin American community, elucidating the potential of Superchain within the Web3 ecosystem. I utilize diverse mediums—videos, reels, AMAs—to showcase projects from Optimism and blockchains using the OP Stack. Every piece of content I create is designed to further education and encourage adoption.
